---
version: 1
op: attend.rerank
description: rerank N candidates by relevance to a query
max_output_tokens: 100
vars: [query, candidates]
---
Rank the candidates by relevance to the query. Most relevant FIRST.

Query: {{.query}}

Candidates (one per line, ID-prefixed):
{{.candidates}}

Output ONLY a JSON object — no prose, no markdown fence. List IDs from MOST to LEAST relevant. Omit candidates that are clearly irrelevant. Keep reason terse (≤10 words).

{"ranking": ["id1", "id2", ...], "reason": "1-line why"}

Example: {"ranking":["jwt_handler","auth_module"],"reason":"jwt_handler directly answers token-expiry question"}
